name: https://gisservices.dorchestercounty.net/arcgis/rest/services
description: A comprehensive web mapping application that contains multiple layers from various sources. Includes evacuation zones, critical area zones, floodplain zones, protected lands, zoning, and parcel boundaries. Also features Dorchester County Council District Map, Zoning Map, Critical Area Map, Floodplain Map, Survey Benchmarks Map, Protected Lands Map, Addressing Hub, Dorchester RoadView, and access to GIS data downloads.
